name: Royal Set
description:
The "Royal Set" Case color: Black *Quantity: 12pcs brushes *Brush type: for face, for eyes, for eyebrow, for eyelash, for lips etc. *Soft and comfortable for use, perfectly for both Studio and Personal use. * Comes with a handy and portable roll up leather case *With proper care, your brushes can be enjoyed for years.

"Royal Set" *1 - Chisel Powder - Great for all over powder and for blending/highlighting the face. *1- Oval Shadow - The ultimate tool for applying any type of shadow *1 - Oval Fluff - Created to blend, shade, or contour shadow on the eyelid. * 1 - Oval Concealer - Excellent for applying liquid or cream based products. * 1 - Soft Fan - This unique tool is great for highlighting with blush and bronze. Also may be used for whisking away excess powder from under the eye. *1 - Angle Liner - Perfect for developing a smooth precise line on your eye. Also great for defining your brows. *1 - Round Crease - Ideal for contouring and shading eye shadow in the crease of your eye lid. *1 - Pointed Liner - Fabulous for the most precise line. *1 - Spoolie - Brilliant for separating lashes for thicker longer lashes. *1 - Brow/Lash Groomer - Created to groom and shape your brows and lashes. *1 - Flocked Sponge - Best used for cream or liquid eyeshadow

name: Glam Gloss "Elite Red"
description:
Glam Gloss "Elite Red"  is a smooth silky texture gloss/lipstick that glides on with definite color and infused with antioxidants. It contains Vitamin E, Beeswax and Wool Oil, so its definitely healthy for your lips.

Glam Gloss is not your ordinary lipstick! "Its the GLAM & Color hue of a lipstick, but has the moisturizing SILK feel of a GLOSS" 

*Glam Gloss*
